  • public class MomentTensor
extends java.lang.Object
    Moment Tensor
    Global CMT 1:Mrr 2:Mtt 3:Mpp 4:M rt 5:Mrp 6 Mtp
    DSM 1:Mrr 2:Mrt 3:Mrp 4:Mtt 5:M tp 6:Mpp

    This class is IMMUTABLE.
